## Gender x Survival


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
merged_data %>% 
  mutate(survived = case_when(
    survived == "D" ~"Decreased",
    survived == "S" ~"Survived",
    TRUE ~ survived
  )) %>% 
  group_by(sex, survived) %>% 
  mutate(sex_survived = n()) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  select(sex, survived, sex_survived) %>% 
  unique() %>% 
  ggplot(aes(
    x=sex,
    y=sex_survived,
    fill=survived
  ))+
  geom_col()+
  labs(
    title= "Survival by Gender",
    x= "Gender",
    y= "Survival",
    fill= "Attribute"
  )+
  geom_text(aes(
    label=sex_survived
  ),
  position=position_stack(vjust=0.8))+
  theme(
    plot.title.position = "plot",
    plot.title = element_text(margin=margin(t=10,b=20)),
    axis.title.x = element_text(margin=margin(t=10))
  )+
  scale_y_continuous(expand=c(0,0),
                     limits=c(0,300))
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](gender-Analysis_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-4-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


## Gender x Ticket Class


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
merged_data %>% 
  mutate(pclass = as.character(pclass)) %>% 
  group_by(sex, pclass) %>% 
  mutate(sex_pclass = n()) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  group_by(sex) %>% 
  mutate(sex_count = n()) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  select(sex, sex_count, pclass, sex_pclass) %>% 
  unique() %>% 
  arrange(pclass) %>% 
  barchart_gg_custom(.,sex,sex_pclass,pclass)+
  labs(
    title= "Ticket Class by Gender",
    x= "Gender",
    y= "Ticket Class",
    fill= "Attribute"
  )+
  geom_text(aes(
    label= paste0(
      sex_pclass,
      " (",
      round((sex_pclass/sex_count)*100,1),
      "%)"
    )
  ),
  position = position_stack(vjust=0.8)
  )+
  theme(
    plot.title.position = "plot",
    plot.title = element_text(margin= margin(t=10,b=20)),
    axis.title.x = element_text(margin= margin(t=10)) 
  )+
  scale_y_continuous(expand=c(0,0),
                     limits=c(0,300))
```
